  "body": "## Problem\r\nCurrent validation includes error messages depending on input. The UI components currently don't adapt to word entry/validation; they are expected to. The copy can reuse keys in the translation file.\r\n\r\n- [x] Issue 1\r\nCurrent: \"checksum for mnemonic seed is invalid\"\r\nExpected: Next button should be disabled when anything other than 12, 15, 18, 21, 24 words are entered. In this error becomes redundant\r\n\r\n- [x] Issue 2\r\nCurrent: Checkmark by word count remains grey when correct number has been reached\r\nExpected: Check mark and word count turns black when correct word count is reached\r\n\r\n- [x] Issue 3\r\nCurrent: Button to continue is blue when a character is entered\r\nExpected: Button to continue is blue when minimum number of words (i.e. 12) is entered\r\n\r\n- [x] Issue 4\r\nCurrent: \"Word x not found in the dictionary\"\r\nExpected: \"Invalid seed phrase. This seed phrase doesn't match our supported dictionary. Check for misspelled words\"\r\nKey: custom-seed-phrase\r\nKey: custom-seed-phrase-text-1\r\n\r\n- [x] Issue 5\r\nCurrent: Error persists when invalid seed phrase is removed\r\nExpected: Error disappears on backspace \r\n\r\n\r\n",
